---
import "../../../public/css/commercialHp/commercialHp1.css";
---

<section id="commercialHpIntro" class="cmhp-section">
    <div class="pin-wrapper">
        <div class="cmhp-intro__content">
            <div class="cmhp-intro__title parallax parallax-op" data-depth="0.4">
                <div class="cmhp-heading lg split--chars">
                    <div>커머셜 홈페이지, </div>
                    <div><span class="color-or">왜 </span> 지금 필요한가요?</div>
                </div>
                <div class="cmhp-desc split--lines">
                    <p>지금 운영 중인 홈페이지, <span class="brx"></span>우리 회사의 목적에 맞게 작동하고 있나요?</p>
                    <p>많은 기업들이 여전히 디자인 중심의 <span class="brx"></span>소개형 홈페이지에 머물러 있습니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cmhp-intro__images">
                <div class="cmhp-intro__person parallax" data-depth="0.6" data-direction="left">
                    <div class="person__img">
                        <div class="person__img-inner"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="person__txt">
                        <div class="speech-bubble split--words" data-direction="left">단순한 정보제공?</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cmhp-intro__person parallax" data-depth="0.8" data-direction="right">
                    <div class="person__img">
                        <div class="person__img-inner"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="person__txt">
                        <div class="speech-bubble split--words" data-direction="right">회사 소개?</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<script>
    import "../../../public/js/commercialHp/commercialHp1.js";
</script>
